@node "Tooltypes" "Tooltypes"

                          Tooltypes


 - DONOTWAIT

    will utilized about Packmaster into the wbstartup to starts 

 - APPICON=(ja|nein)

    ja        Packmaster starts as AppIcon (icon on workbench)
    nein      Packmaster starts with main window (Appmenu=nein)

 - APPMENU=(ja|nein)

    ja        Packmaster starts as AppMenu (Menuitem into toolsmenu)
    nein      Packmaster starts with main window (Appicon=nein)

        APPICON and APPMENU there are also combinated (both=ja)

 - PGPTMP=(ja|nein)

    ja        saved keyfile content temporarily (speedup by one read by
              some PGP functions)
              Here must APPICON=nein and APPMENU=nein !
    nein      keyfile content is not temporarily saved
@endnode

@node "Shortcuts" "Shortcuts"

                            @{u}Shortcuts@{uu}


                @{b}RA@{ub} = right Amiga Button

 @{b}RA@{ub} A = Delete Archive
 @{b}RA@{ub} B = Quit
 @{b}RA@{ub} C = Testing
 @{b}RA@{ub} D = External
 @{b}RA@{ub} E = Unpack
 @{b}RA@{ub} F = Insert File into Archive
 @{b}RA@{ub} G = Content
 @{b}RA@{ub} H = Help (also with Help accessable)
 @{b}RA@{ub} I = Information
 @{b}RA@{ub} K = Copy Archive
 @{b}RA@{ub} L = Delete File from Archive
 @{b}RA@{ub} M = Sleep
 @{b}RA@{ub} O = File Copy
 @{b}RA@{ub} P = Pack
 @{b}RA@{ub} S = Setup save
 @{b}RA@{ub} U = Content as File
 @{b}RA@{ub} V = Unpack File from Archive
 @{b}RA@{ub} W = Internal
 @{b}RA@{ub} Y = Setup load
 @{b}RA@{ub} 1 = Encrypt (PGP)
 @{b}RA@{ub} 2 = Decode (PGP)
 @{b}RA@{ub} 3 = Database sign (PGP)
 @{b}RA@{ub} 4 = Content dump (PGP)
 @{b}RA@{ub} 5 = Make key  (PGP)
 @{b}RA@{ub} 6 = Edit Key (PGP)
 @{b}RA@{ub} 7 = Sign Key (PGP)
 @{b}RA@{ub} 8 = Add Key (PGP)
 @{b}RA@{ub} 9 = Copy Key Out Keyfile (PGP)
 @{b}RA@{ub} 0 = Del Key (PGP)
 @{b}RA@{ub} # = Del Key Sign (PGP)
 @{b}RA@{ub} * = Dump Fingerprint (PGP)
 @{b}RA@{ub} + = Save Key ASCII (PGP)
 @{b}RA@{ub} - = Backtrack Key (PGP)
@endnode

